{"tid":1534670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"阻人道救援，禽獸不如！ - 高慧然","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:32:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:42:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6518a063d01c0a3deb97db96b2520737decacfe7","tid":1534670,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:32:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190903/20760728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760728&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFKpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=56991de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190903%2F20760728&h=8ce81a9b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20190903/20760728</a><br />\n<br />\n阻人道救援，禽獸不如！ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190903/large/1567408020_bfe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190903%2Flarge%2F1567408020_bfe4.jpg&h=e0fdf8da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n831當晚，太子地鐵站一群急救員被攔在鐵閘外的視頻一定要傳播開去，讓國際媒體播放，讓全世界人知道香港警察禽獸不如，以執法為名公然犯法！<br />\n<br />\n我只敢看一遍，硬着頭皮逼自己往下看，眼淚不受控地流，完全能夠想像現場急救員的焦慮、擔憂、憤怒、無助、不甘，以及極度不解，香港怎麼變成這樣？<br />\n<br />\n一個急救員在鐵閘外嘶啞着喉嚨苦苦哀求，「你俾我入去救佢啊阿sir，我救完佢你打我、你射我、你拉我都好啊，我求求你俾我入去救佢啊！」邊哀求邊哭出聲來，急救員看到的傷者應該情況很危急。後面有紛亂人聲，有人罵警察，有人大嗌：「人命嚟㗎！」但急救員始終被拒之鐵閘外，最後跟其他急救員抱頭，無助痛哭。對急救員來說，一門之隔，眼見有人受傷掙扎而被拒絕向傷者施救，應是職業生涯中永難忘懷的痛。<br />\n<br />\n受傷的人，若不及時施救，重則失救死亡，輕則傷殘，造成一世後遺症。太子地鐵站內的傷者，無非是示威者甚至是普通乘客，即使是作奸犯科的江洋大盜，也應獲得人道救援，他所犯罪行，交由法庭審判，自有法律制裁。警察的職責，是以最低武力捉拿疑犯，後面的事情交由法庭去做。把連疑犯都不是的巿民打成重傷，然後阻止急救員施救這是嚴重的人道罪行，這樣的警隊，已經失去執法的公信力，跟恐怖分子，跟納粹有分別嗎？林鄭治下，縱容出這樣一支警隊，林鄭及整個管治團隊同樣觸犯人道罪行，必將遭到懲罰！ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n我們與死的距離 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n那香港賊婆娘在說什麼？ (古德明)"},{"pid":"eba09e09e326ace4b5dfa2e90afb111a150651b4","tid":1534670,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"813a49d3e9569a6c37e4110b9708faf40744e6f5","tid":1534670,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:42:41.000Z","msg":"popo身有屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />延遲治療點解唔可以告酷刑罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電